{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u7ad48456\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的第二个参数是依赖项数组，React 通过它来判断是否需要重新执行 effect。判断依赖是否发生变化的核心机制是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">浅比较</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，具体规则如下：</span></p><hr id=\"uDdfn\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"RIqzL\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 比较时机</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ubb799edf\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">每次组件渲染完成后（即 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">commit 阶段的 layout 之后，浏览器绘制之前</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">），React 会检查该 effect 的依赖项数组。</span></li><li id=\"u64f4db81\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">首次渲染</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（mount），直接执行 effect 并记录依赖项。</span></li><li id=\"ue0fbf7df\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">更新渲染</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（update），React 会将当前传入的依赖项与上一次渲染时记录的依赖项进行逐个比较。</span></li></ul><hr id=\"FjCKB\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"Cf3Os\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 比较方法：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code></h2><p id=\"u61c10ce3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 来比较每个依赖项的新旧值。</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的行为与 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">===</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 基本一致，但有两个特殊处理：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6fc1f818\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，但 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u2a16e29d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">+0 === -0</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，但 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li></ul><p id=\"u1b519fd4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">因此，当依赖项是原始类型（string、number、boolean、null、undefined）时，比较结果与 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">===</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 几乎相同；当依赖项是引用类型（对象、数组、函数）时，比较的是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">引用地址</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">是否相同，而不是内容是否相等。</span></p><hr id=\"vHkjJ\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"nWlF1\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 判断规则</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u5d01e67a\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">所有依赖项</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的新值与旧值都相同（即每个依赖项的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 比较结果都为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），React 认为依赖未变化，</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">跳过本次 effect 的执行</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u4196a85e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">任意一个依赖项</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的新值与旧值不同（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 返回 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），React 认为依赖已变化，会先执行上一次 effect 的清理函数（如果存在），然后执行新的 effect。</span></li></ul><hr id=\"qQd4S\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"Wm28N\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4. 特殊情况</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uc814f3a4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">空依赖数组 </span></strong><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：因为没有任何依赖项，比较结果永远为“无变化”，所以 effect 只在首次渲染后执行一次，后续更新永远跳过。</span></li><li id=\"u5452fe32\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">不传第二个参数</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 effect（先清理再执行）。</span></li></ul><hr id=\"lAUsF\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"kOvgx\"><span class=\"ne-text\">5. 示例说明</span></h2><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"ZWgbP\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>const [count, setCount] = useState(0);\nuseEffect(() =&gt; {\n  document.title = `You clicked ${count} times`;\n}, [count]); // 依赖项为 count</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub4f11fa3\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">首次渲染：记录依赖项 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[0]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，执行 effect。</span></li><li id=\"u9ae0eb09\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击按钮，</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">setCount(1)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 触发重渲染：新依赖项 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[1]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，与旧值 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[0]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 比较 → </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(1, 0)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，依赖变化，重新执行 effect。</span></li><li id=\"u28d30164\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果依赖项是对象：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"DyXHx\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>const [user, setUser] = useState({ name: 'Alice' });\nuseEffect(() =&gt; {\n  console.log(user.name);\n}, [user]);</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u29e0cfd4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">即使 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">user</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对象内容不变，但调用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">setUser({ name: 'Alice' })</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 传入新对象时，新旧引用不同，</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 返回 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，effect 会执行。这可能导致不必要的 effect 执行，因此需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useMemo</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useCallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></li></ul></ul><hr id=\"XrRnx\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"lHp1R\"><span class=\"ne-text\">6. 依赖项存储位置</span></h2><p id=\"ued482cbb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 在内部将每个 effect 的信息（包括上一次的依赖项）存储在对应 Fiber 节点的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">memoizedState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 链表中。每个 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对应一个 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Effect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对象，其中包含：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uf268647b\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">create</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: effect 函数</span></li><li id=\"ue600ba12\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">destroy</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: 清理函数</span></li><li id=\"u031d1a7b\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">deps</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: 上一次的依赖项数组</span></li><li id=\"ua022a2ec\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">next</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: 指向下一个 effect 的指针</span></li></ul><p id=\"ueeae5ccc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更新时，React 从链表中取出上一次的依赖项，与当前传入的依赖项进行 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 比较。</span></p><hr id=\"i0fqj\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"j86Wl\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h2><p id=\"u8f1ad501\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的依赖比较基于 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 进行浅比较</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，只有所有依赖项都与上一次相同时才跳过 effect。理解这一机制有助于避免因引用变化导致的无限循环，以及优化 effect 的执行频率。</span></p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u7ad48456\" id=\"u7ad48456\"><code data-lake-id=\"ueab69f3d\" id=\"ueab69f3d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc3c2005\" id=\"ufc3c2005\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uba265f87\" id=\"uba265f87\"> 的第二个参数是依赖项数组，React 通过它来判断是否需要重新执行 effect。判断依赖是否发生变化的核心机制是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b908b01\" id=\"u5b908b01\">浅比较</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u937cf9f2\" id=\"u937cf9f2\">，具体规则如下：</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22uDdfn%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"RIqzL\" id=\"RIqzL\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab1bee3d\" id=\"uab1bee3d\">1. 比较时机</span></h2><ul list=\"u1d484119\"><li fid=\"u12c06899\" data-lake-id=\"ubb799edf\" id=\"ubb799edf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5745149d\" id=\"u5745149d\">每次组件渲染完成后（即 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3a989096\" id=\"u3a989096\">commit 阶段的 layout 之后，浏览器绘制之前</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u893b6ed7\" id=\"u893b6ed7\">），React 会检查该 effect 的依赖项数组。</span></li><li fid=\"u12c06899\" data-lake-id=\"u64f4db81\" id=\"u64f4db81\"><span data-lake-id=\"uabf6cf4d\" id=\"uabf6cf4d\">如果是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9a313807\" id=\"u9a313807\">首次渲染</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc7ab0d9d\" id=\"uc7ab0d9d\">（mount），直接执行 effect 并记录依赖项。</span></li><li fid=\"u12c06899\" data-lake-id=\"ue0fbf7df\" id=\"ue0fbf7df\"><span data-lake-id=\"u635e69b7\" id=\"u635e69b7\">如果是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3035a700\" id=\"u3035a700\">更新渲染</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1c152209\" id=\"u1c152209\">（update），React 会将当前传入的依赖项与上一次渲染时记录的依赖项进行逐个比较。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22FjCKB%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"Cf3Os\" id=\"Cf3Os\"><span data-lake-id=\"u68cf8d80\" id=\"u68cf8d80\">2. 比较方法：</span><code data-lake-id=\"ud6b3a534\" id=\"ud6b3a534\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7fda3ec7\" id=\"u7fda3ec7\">Object.is</span></code></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u61c10ce3\" id=\"u61c10ce3\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf393d462\" id=\"uf393d462\">React 使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u31424e56\" id=\"u31424e56\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua780ff8e\" id=\"ua780ff8e\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u51aa7e0a\" id=\"u51aa7e0a\"> 来比较每个依赖项的新旧值。</span><code data-lake-id=\"u05a1b877\" id=\"u05a1b877\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucc6bea84\" id=\"ucc6bea84\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u38d9f227\" id=\"u38d9f227\"> 的行为与 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ucba83e6b\" id=\"ucba83e6b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u60ab663f\" id=\"u60ab663f\">===</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6e161916\" id=\"u6e161916\"> 基本一致，但有两个特殊处理：</span></p><ul list=\"ue88c09ae\"><li fid=\"u2dd8ca08\" data-lake-id=\"u6fc1f818\" id=\"u6fc1f818\"><code data-lake-id=\"u661042b0\" id=\"u661042b0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u28a14289\" id=\"u28a14289\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0800e5bf\" id=\"u0800e5bf\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ueb0ae64a\" id=\"ueb0ae64a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u04d37001\" id=\"u04d37001\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uaa9571c9\" id=\"uaa9571c9\">，但 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u978daab4\" id=\"u978daab4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u64e53310\" id=\"u64e53310\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5cff569e\" id=\"u5cff569e\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ubbf16aa7\" id=\"ubbf16aa7\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua4b2dc06\" id=\"ua4b2dc06\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue129307d\" id=\"ue129307d\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u2dd8ca08\" data-lake-id=\"u2a16e29d\" id=\"u2a16e29d\"><code data-lake-id=\"u1b8bc6d1\" id=\"u1b8bc6d1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2a83df4a\" id=\"u2a83df4a\">+0 === -0</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6ecad28f\" id=\"u6ecad28f\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1c04f7f5\" id=\"u1c04f7f5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5faa5f1e\" id=\"u5faa5f1e\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7a661c44\" id=\"u7a661c44\">，但 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u51968b69\" id=\"u51968b69\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue9fa0b24\" id=\"ue9fa0b24\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u736ba8ee\" id=\"u736ba8ee\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8bebeced\" id=\"u8bebeced\"><span data-lake-id=\"uddce5f97\" id=\"uddce5f97\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uaa6fad67\" id=\"uaa6fad67\">。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u1b519fd4\" id=\"u1b519fd4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u029dc1d1\" id=\"u029dc1d1\">因此，当依赖项是原始类型（string、number、boolean、null、undefined）时，比较结果与 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u7fa10aaf\" id=\"u7fa10aaf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0c9a3a30\" id=\"u0c9a3a30\">===</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udb5ac74e\" id=\"udb5ac74e\"> 几乎相同；当依赖项是引用类型（对象、数组、函数）时，比较的是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufa6e47da\" id=\"ufa6e47da\">引用地址</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6a23fa00\" id=\"u6a23fa00\">是否相同，而不是内容是否相等。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22vHkjJ%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"nWlF1\" id=\"nWlF1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u15dc157f\" id=\"u15dc157f\">3. 判断规则</span></h2><ul list=\"uf8e5db73\"><li fid=\"u5dee1c05\" data-lake-id=\"u5d01e67a\" id=\"u5d01e67a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub86eb3a7\" id=\"ub86eb3a7\">如果</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3e704c4a\" id=\"u3e704c4a\">所有依赖项</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4fa8d998\" id=\"u4fa8d998\">的新值与旧值都相同（即每个依赖项的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6deef289\" id=\"u6deef289\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub2e23dab\" id=\"ub2e23dab\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1911e692\" id=\"u1911e692\"> 比较结果都为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"udb691ae9\" id=\"udb691ae9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4088bcce\" id=\"u4088bcce\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u93632bc0\" id=\"u93632bc0\">），React 认为依赖未变化，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf25097d5\" id=\"uf25097d5\">跳过本次 effect 的执行</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u14f2e22b\" id=\"u14f2e22b\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u5dee1c05\" data-lake-id=\"u4196a85e\" id=\"u4196a85e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u075ae6f4\" id=\"u075ae6f4\">如果</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7059f63d\" id=\"u7059f63d\">任意一个依赖项</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u56246715\" id=\"u56246715\">的新值与旧值不同（</span><code data-lake-id=\"u1fb82d2f\" id=\"u1fb82d2f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u576c5c75\" id=\"u576c5c75\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u04ea626c\" id=\"u04ea626c\"> 返回 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u85c401a7\" id=\"u85c401a7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u56daae77\" id=\"u56daae77\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3fe36b9e\" id=\"u3fe36b9e\">），React 认为依赖已变化，会先执行上一次 effect 的清理函数（如果存在），然后执行新的 effect。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22qQd4S%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"Wm28N\" id=\"Wm28N\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaee9f810\" id=\"uaee9f810\">4. 特殊情况</span></h2><ul list=\"ue78e8da2\"><li fid=\"ud7c6aa89\" data-lake-id=\"uc814f3a4\" id=\"uc814f3a4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8cc14d6c\" id=\"u8cc14d6c\">空依赖数组 </span></strong><code data-lake-id=\"u7be589f0\" id=\"u7be589f0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u20c01007\" id=\"u20c01007\">[]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc5542511\" id=\"uc5542511\">：因为没有任何依赖项，比较结果永远为“无变化”，所以 effect 只在首次渲染后执行一次，后续更新永远跳过。</span></li><li fid=\"ud7c6aa89\" data-lake-id=\"u5452fe32\" id=\"u5452fe32\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1a7dd4f1\" id=\"u1a7dd4f1\">不传第二个参数</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubbd3761c\" id=\"ubbd3761c\">：相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 effect（先清理再执行）。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22lAUsF%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"kOvgx\" id=\"kOvgx\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub7ff75d0\" id=\"ub7ff75d0\">5. 示例说明</span></h2><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20%5Bcount%2C%20setCount%5D%20%3D%20useState(0)%3B%5CnuseEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20document.title%20%3D%20%60You%20clicked%20%24%7Bcount%7D%20times%60%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20%5Bcount%5D)%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%BA%20count%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22ZWgbP%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"u45eea085\"><li fid=\"u9b71f4dd\" data-lake-id=\"ub4f11fa3\" id=\"ub4f11fa3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4fba316e\" id=\"u4fba316e\">首次渲染：记录依赖项 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1090a3c\" id=\"ua1090a3c\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufe850195\" id=\"ufe850195\">[0]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucba963af\" id=\"ucba963af\">，执行 effect。</span></li><li fid=\"u9b71f4dd\" data-lake-id=\"u9ae0eb09\" id=\"u9ae0eb09\"><span data-lake-id=\"u192d0ac9\" id=\"u192d0ac9\">点击按钮，</span><code data-lake-id=\"uefa61cd7\" id=\"uefa61cd7\"><span data-lake-id=\"uce0f0c8f\" id=\"uce0f0c8f\">setCount(1)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5aa075a1\" id=\"u5aa075a1\"> 触发重渲染：新依赖项 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9ab06c88\" id=\"u9ab06c88\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1ceaadd7\" id=\"u1ceaadd7\">[1]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0397b7ed\" id=\"u0397b7ed\">，与旧值 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6c095993\" id=\"u6c095993\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7bf15a9c\" id=\"u7bf15a9c\">[0]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6a9df655\" id=\"u6a9df655\"> 比较 → </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1a7447a\" id=\"ua1a7447a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u22a8bd8b\" id=\"u22a8bd8b\">Object.is(1, 0)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u98dc22ca\" id=\"u98dc22ca\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua9f71189\" id=\"ua9f71189\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5e3a402e\" id=\"u5e3a402e\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf9c00876\" id=\"uf9c00876\">，依赖变化，重新执行 effect。</span></li><li fid=\"u9b71f4dd\" data-lake-id=\"u28d30164\" id=\"u28d30164\"><span data-lake-id=\"u734e8585\" id=\"u734e8585\">如果依赖项是对象：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20%5Buser%2C%20setUser%5D%20%3D%20useState(%7B%20name%3A%20'Alice'%20%7D)%3B%5CnuseEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20console.log(user.name)%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20%5Buser%5D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22DyXHx%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"u45eea085\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u94103bab\" data-lake-id=\"u29e0cfd4\" id=\"u29e0cfd4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1ff85bd1\" id=\"u1ff85bd1\">即使 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u4a3601f3\" id=\"u4a3601f3\"><span data-lake-id=\"uda826b49\" id=\"uda826b49\">user</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3addc8e8\" id=\"u3addc8e8\"> 对象内容不变，但调用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5d512ee3\" id=\"u5d512ee3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u28acaf1b\" id=\"u28acaf1b\">setUser({ name: 'Alice' })</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8519654e\" id=\"u8519654e\"> 传入新对象时，新旧引用不同，</span><code data-lake-id=\"u6fda6d30\" id=\"u6fda6d30\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5afc5699\" id=\"u5afc5699\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u70e69b45\" id=\"u70e69b45\"> 返回 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u36d198d6\" id=\"u36d198d6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9a9eae35\" id=\"u9a9eae35\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0511cde3\" id=\"u0511cde3\">，effect 会执行。这可能导致不必要的 effect 执行，因此需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u17829656\" id=\"u17829656\"><span data-lake-id=\"u005de315\" id=\"u005de315\">useMemo</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uae503473\" id=\"uae503473\">/</span><code data-lake-id=\"uc86b6bf6\" id=\"uc86b6bf6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u79eded00\" id=\"u79eded00\">useCallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue7e25048\" id=\"ue7e25048\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22XrRnx%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"lHp1R\" id=\"lHp1R\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5aa4e3b8\" id=\"u5aa4e3b8\">6. 依赖项存储位置</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"ued482cbb\" id=\"ued482cbb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u28300bff\" id=\"u28300bff\">React 在内部将每个 effect 的信息（包括上一次的依赖项）存储在对应 Fiber 节点的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u93d6a325\" id=\"u93d6a325\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc6c0ef97\" id=\"uc6c0ef97\">memoizedState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u84f6b433\" id=\"u84f6b433\"> 链表中。每个 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufc626ec4\" id=\"ufc626ec4\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubb02899d\" id=\"ubb02899d\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u009f0264\" id=\"u009f0264\"> 对应一个 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u12df8b14\" id=\"u12df8b14\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0ce715fb\" id=\"u0ce715fb\">Effect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8172c240\" id=\"u8172c240\"> 对象，其中包含：</span></p><ul list=\"u363bfaaf\"><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"uf268647b\" id=\"uf268647b\"><code data-lake-id=\"u2b1649e4\" id=\"u2b1649e4\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub398da4c\" id=\"ub398da4c\">create</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0625b798\" id=\"u0625b798\">: effect 函数</span></li><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"ue600ba12\" id=\"ue600ba12\"><code data-lake-id=\"u61b507f9\" id=\"u61b507f9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5c01751b\" id=\"u5c01751b\">destroy</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uea2e354c\" id=\"uea2e354c\">: 清理函数</span></li><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"u031d1a7b\" id=\"u031d1a7b\"><code data-lake-id=\"u1f7b1e03\" id=\"u1f7b1e03\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue8b04c0e\" id=\"ue8b04c0e\">deps</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u960541d1\" id=\"u960541d1\">: 上一次的依赖项数组</span></li><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"ua022a2ec\" id=\"ua022a2ec\"><code data-lake-id=\"ue79994ec\" id=\"ue79994ec\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5c01f9c8\" id=\"u5c01f9c8\">next</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u85e0af87\" id=\"u85e0af87\">: 指向下一个 effect 的指针</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ueeae5ccc\" id=\"ueeae5ccc\"><span data-lake-id=\"uedb40b99\" id=\"uedb40b99\">更新时，React 从链表中取出上一次的依赖项，与当前传入的依赖项进行 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1c71b332\" id=\"u1c71b332\"><span data-lake-id=\"u724c0119\" id=\"u724c0119\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u35bf5656\" id=\"u35bf5656\"> 比较。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22i0fqj%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"j86Wl\" id=\"j86Wl\"><span data-lake-id=\"u06a74311\" id=\"u06a74311\">总结</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u8f1ad501\" id=\"u8f1ad501\"><code data-lake-id=\"ub0a31a13\" id=\"ub0a31a13\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue2a3f0c4\" id=\"ue2a3f0c4\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2f77f7e8\" id=\"u2f77f7e8\"> 的依赖比较基于 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u145c5603\" id=\"u145c5603\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc523c3cc\" id=\"uc523c3cc\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u66b34a00\" id=\"u66b34a00\"> 进行浅比较</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"udcd90429\" id=\"udcd90429\">，只有所有依赖项都与上一次相同时才跳过 effect。理解这一机制有助于避免因引用变化导致的无限循环，以及优化 effect 的执行频率。</span></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u7ad48456\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的第二个参数是依赖项数组，React 通过它来判断是否需要重新执行 effect。判断依赖是否发生变化的核心机制是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">浅比较</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，具体规则如下：</span></p><hr id=\"uDdfn\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"RIqzL\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 比较时机</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ubb799edf\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">每次组件渲染完成后（即 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">commit 阶段的 layout 之后，浏览器绘制之前</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">），React 会检查该 effect 的依赖项数组。</span></li><li id=\"u64f4db81\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">首次渲染</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（mount），直接执行 effect 并记录依赖项。</span></li><li id=\"ue0fbf7df\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">更新渲染</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（update），React 会将当前传入的依赖项与上一次渲染时记录的依赖项进行逐个比较。</span></li></ul><hr id=\"FjCKB\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"Cf3Os\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 比较方法：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code></h2><p id=\"u61c10ce3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 来比较每个依赖项的新旧值。</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的行为与 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">===</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 基本一致，但有两个特殊处理：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6fc1f818\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，但 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u2a16e29d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">+0 === -0</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，但 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li></ul><p id=\"u1b519fd4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">因此，当依赖项是原始类型（string、number、boolean、null、undefined）时，比较结果与 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">===</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 几乎相同；当依赖项是引用类型（对象、数组、函数）时，比较的是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">引用地址</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">是否相同，而不是内容是否相等。</span></p><hr id=\"vHkjJ\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"nWlF1\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 判断规则</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u5d01e67a\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">所有依赖项</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的新值与旧值都相同（即每个依赖项的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 比较结果都为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），React 认为依赖未变化，</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">跳过本次 effect 的执行</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></li><li id=\"u4196a85e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">任意一个依赖项</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">的新值与旧值不同（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 返回 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），React 认为依赖已变化，会先执行上一次 effect 的清理函数（如果存在），然后执行新的 effect。</span></li></ul><hr id=\"qQd4S\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"Wm28N\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4. 特殊情况</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uc814f3a4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">空依赖数组 </span></strong><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：因为没有任何依赖项，比较结果永远为“无变化”，所以 effect 只在首次渲染后执行一次，后续更新永远跳过。</span></li><li id=\"u5452fe32\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">不传第二个参数</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 effect（先清理再执行）。</span></li></ul><hr id=\"lAUsF\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"kOvgx\"><span class=\"ne-text\">5. 示例说明</span></h2><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"ZWgbP\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>const [count, setCount] = useState(0);\nuseEffect(() =&gt; {\n  document.title = `You clicked ${count} times`;\n}, [count]); // 依赖项为 count</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub4f11fa3\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">首次渲染：记录依赖项 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[0]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，执行 effect。</span></li><li id=\"u9ae0eb09\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击按钮，</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">setCount(1)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 触发重渲染：新依赖项 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[1]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，与旧值 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">[0]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 比较 → </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is(1, 0)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，依赖变化，重新执行 effect。</span></li><li id=\"u28d30164\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果依赖项是对象：</span></li></ul><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"DyXHx\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>const [user, setUser] = useState({ name: 'Alice' });\nuseEffect(() =&gt; {\n  console.log(user.name);\n}, [user]);</code></pre><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u29e0cfd4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">即使 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">user</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对象内容不变，但调用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">setUser({ name: 'Alice' })</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 传入新对象时，新旧引用不同，</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 返回 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，effect 会执行。这可能导致不必要的 effect 执行，因此需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useMemo</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useCallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></li></ul></ul><hr id=\"XrRnx\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"lHp1R\"><span class=\"ne-text\">6. 依赖项存储位置</span></h2><p id=\"ued482cbb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 在内部将每个 effect 的信息（包括上一次的依赖项）存储在对应 Fiber 节点的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">memoizedState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 链表中。每个 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对应一个 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Effect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 对象，其中包含：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uf268647b\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">create</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: effect 函数</span></li><li id=\"ue600ba12\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">destroy</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: 清理函数</span></li><li id=\"u031d1a7b\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">deps</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: 上一次的依赖项数组</span></li><li id=\"ua022a2ec\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">next</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">: 指向下一个 effect 的指针</span></li></ul><p id=\"ueeae5ccc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更新时，React 从链表中取出上一次的依赖项，与当前传入的依赖项进行 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 比较。</span></p><hr id=\"i0fqj\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h2 id=\"j86Wl\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h2><p id=\"u8f1ad501\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">useEffect</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的依赖比较基于 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 进行浅比较</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，只有所有依赖项都与上一次相同时才跳过 effect。理解这一机制有助于避免因引用变化导致的无限循环，以及优化 effect 的执行频率。</span></p></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u7ad48456\" id=\"u7ad48456\"><code data-lake-id=\"ueab69f3d\" id=\"ueab69f3d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc3c2005\" id=\"ufc3c2005\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uba265f87\" id=\"uba265f87\"> 的第二个参数是依赖项数组，React 通过它来判断是否需要重新执行 effect。判断依赖是否发生变化的核心机制是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b908b01\" id=\"u5b908b01\">浅比较</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u937cf9f2\" id=\"u937cf9f2\">，具体规则如下：</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22uDdfn%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"RIqzL\" id=\"RIqzL\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab1bee3d\" id=\"uab1bee3d\">1. 比较时机</span></h2><ul list=\"u1d484119\"><li fid=\"u12c06899\" data-lake-id=\"ubb799edf\" id=\"ubb799edf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5745149d\" id=\"u5745149d\">每次组件渲染完成后（即 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3a989096\" id=\"u3a989096\">commit 阶段的 layout 之后，浏览器绘制之前</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u893b6ed7\" id=\"u893b6ed7\">），React 会检查该 effect 的依赖项数组。</span></li><li fid=\"u12c06899\" data-lake-id=\"u64f4db81\" id=\"u64f4db81\"><span data-lake-id=\"uabf6cf4d\" id=\"uabf6cf4d\">如果是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9a313807\" id=\"u9a313807\">首次渲染</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc7ab0d9d\" id=\"uc7ab0d9d\">（mount），直接执行 effect 并记录依赖项。</span></li><li fid=\"u12c06899\" data-lake-id=\"ue0fbf7df\" id=\"ue0fbf7df\"><span data-lake-id=\"u635e69b7\" id=\"u635e69b7\">如果是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3035a700\" id=\"u3035a700\">更新渲染</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1c152209\" id=\"u1c152209\">（update），React 会将当前传入的依赖项与上一次渲染时记录的依赖项进行逐个比较。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22FjCKB%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"Cf3Os\" id=\"Cf3Os\"><span data-lake-id=\"u68cf8d80\" id=\"u68cf8d80\">2. 比较方法：</span><code data-lake-id=\"ud6b3a534\" id=\"ud6b3a534\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7fda3ec7\" id=\"u7fda3ec7\">Object.is</span></code></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u61c10ce3\" id=\"u61c10ce3\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf393d462\" id=\"uf393d462\">React 使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u31424e56\" id=\"u31424e56\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua780ff8e\" id=\"ua780ff8e\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u51aa7e0a\" id=\"u51aa7e0a\"> 来比较每个依赖项的新旧值。</span><code data-lake-id=\"u05a1b877\" id=\"u05a1b877\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucc6bea84\" id=\"ucc6bea84\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u38d9f227\" id=\"u38d9f227\"> 的行为与 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ucba83e6b\" id=\"ucba83e6b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u60ab663f\" id=\"u60ab663f\">===</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6e161916\" id=\"u6e161916\"> 基本一致，但有两个特殊处理：</span></p><ul list=\"ue88c09ae\"><li fid=\"u2dd8ca08\" data-lake-id=\"u6fc1f818\" id=\"u6fc1f818\"><code data-lake-id=\"u661042b0\" id=\"u661042b0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u28a14289\" id=\"u28a14289\">NaN === NaN</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0800e5bf\" id=\"u0800e5bf\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ueb0ae64a\" id=\"ueb0ae64a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u04d37001\" id=\"u04d37001\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uaa9571c9\" id=\"uaa9571c9\">，但 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u978daab4\" id=\"u978daab4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u64e53310\" id=\"u64e53310\">Object.is(NaN, NaN)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5cff569e\" id=\"u5cff569e\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ubbf16aa7\" id=\"ubbf16aa7\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua4b2dc06\" id=\"ua4b2dc06\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue129307d\" id=\"ue129307d\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u2dd8ca08\" data-lake-id=\"u2a16e29d\" id=\"u2a16e29d\"><code data-lake-id=\"u1b8bc6d1\" id=\"u1b8bc6d1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2a83df4a\" id=\"u2a83df4a\">+0 === -0</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6ecad28f\" id=\"u6ecad28f\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1c04f7f5\" id=\"u1c04f7f5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5faa5f1e\" id=\"u5faa5f1e\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7a661c44\" id=\"u7a661c44\">，但 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u51968b69\" id=\"u51968b69\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue9fa0b24\" id=\"ue9fa0b24\">Object.is(+0, -0)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u736ba8ee\" id=\"u736ba8ee\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8bebeced\" id=\"u8bebeced\"><span data-lake-id=\"uddce5f97\" id=\"uddce5f97\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uaa6fad67\" id=\"uaa6fad67\">。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u1b519fd4\" id=\"u1b519fd4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u029dc1d1\" id=\"u029dc1d1\">因此，当依赖项是原始类型（string、number、boolean、null、undefined）时，比较结果与 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u7fa10aaf\" id=\"u7fa10aaf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0c9a3a30\" id=\"u0c9a3a30\">===</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udb5ac74e\" id=\"udb5ac74e\"> 几乎相同；当依赖项是引用类型（对象、数组、函数）时，比较的是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufa6e47da\" id=\"ufa6e47da\">引用地址</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6a23fa00\" id=\"u6a23fa00\">是否相同，而不是内容是否相等。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22vHkjJ%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"nWlF1\" id=\"nWlF1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u15dc157f\" id=\"u15dc157f\">3. 判断规则</span></h2><ul list=\"uf8e5db73\"><li fid=\"u5dee1c05\" data-lake-id=\"u5d01e67a\" id=\"u5d01e67a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub86eb3a7\" id=\"ub86eb3a7\">如果</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3e704c4a\" id=\"u3e704c4a\">所有依赖项</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4fa8d998\" id=\"u4fa8d998\">的新值与旧值都相同（即每个依赖项的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6deef289\" id=\"u6deef289\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub2e23dab\" id=\"ub2e23dab\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1911e692\" id=\"u1911e692\"> 比较结果都为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"udb691ae9\" id=\"udb691ae9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4088bcce\" id=\"u4088bcce\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u93632bc0\" id=\"u93632bc0\">），React 认为依赖未变化，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf25097d5\" id=\"uf25097d5\">跳过本次 effect 的执行</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u14f2e22b\" id=\"u14f2e22b\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u5dee1c05\" data-lake-id=\"u4196a85e\" id=\"u4196a85e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u075ae6f4\" id=\"u075ae6f4\">如果</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7059f63d\" id=\"u7059f63d\">任意一个依赖项</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u56246715\" id=\"u56246715\">的新值与旧值不同（</span><code data-lake-id=\"u1fb82d2f\" id=\"u1fb82d2f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u576c5c75\" id=\"u576c5c75\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u04ea626c\" id=\"u04ea626c\"> 返回 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u85c401a7\" id=\"u85c401a7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u56daae77\" id=\"u56daae77\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3fe36b9e\" id=\"u3fe36b9e\">），React 认为依赖已变化，会先执行上一次 effect 的清理函数（如果存在），然后执行新的 effect。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22qQd4S%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"Wm28N\" id=\"Wm28N\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaee9f810\" id=\"uaee9f810\">4. 特殊情况</span></h2><ul list=\"ue78e8da2\"><li fid=\"ud7c6aa89\" data-lake-id=\"uc814f3a4\" id=\"uc814f3a4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8cc14d6c\" id=\"u8cc14d6c\">空依赖数组 </span></strong><code data-lake-id=\"u7be589f0\" id=\"u7be589f0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u20c01007\" id=\"u20c01007\">[]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc5542511\" id=\"uc5542511\">：因为没有任何依赖项，比较结果永远为“无变化”，所以 effect 只在首次渲染后执行一次，后续更新永远跳过。</span></li><li fid=\"ud7c6aa89\" data-lake-id=\"u5452fe32\" id=\"u5452fe32\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1a7dd4f1\" id=\"u1a7dd4f1\">不传第二个参数</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubbd3761c\" id=\"ubbd3761c\">：相当于没有依赖数组，React 会在每次渲染后都执行 effect（先清理再执行）。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22lAUsF%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"kOvgx\" id=\"kOvgx\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub7ff75d0\" id=\"ub7ff75d0\">5. 示例说明</span></h2><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20%5Bcount%2C%20setCount%5D%20%3D%20useState(0)%3B%5CnuseEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20document.title%20%3D%20%60You%20clicked%20%24%7Bcount%7D%20times%60%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20%5Bcount%5D)%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%BA%20count%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22ZWgbP%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"u45eea085\"><li fid=\"u9b71f4dd\" data-lake-id=\"ub4f11fa3\" id=\"ub4f11fa3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4fba316e\" id=\"u4fba316e\">首次渲染：记录依赖项 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1090a3c\" id=\"ua1090a3c\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufe850195\" id=\"ufe850195\">[0]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucba963af\" id=\"ucba963af\">，执行 effect。</span></li><li fid=\"u9b71f4dd\" data-lake-id=\"u9ae0eb09\" id=\"u9ae0eb09\"><span data-lake-id=\"u192d0ac9\" id=\"u192d0ac9\">点击按钮，</span><code data-lake-id=\"uefa61cd7\" id=\"uefa61cd7\"><span data-lake-id=\"uce0f0c8f\" id=\"uce0f0c8f\">setCount(1)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5aa075a1\" id=\"u5aa075a1\"> 触发重渲染：新依赖项 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9ab06c88\" id=\"u9ab06c88\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1ceaadd7\" id=\"u1ceaadd7\">[1]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0397b7ed\" id=\"u0397b7ed\">，与旧值 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6c095993\" id=\"u6c095993\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7bf15a9c\" id=\"u7bf15a9c\">[0]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6a9df655\" id=\"u6a9df655\"> 比较 → </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1a7447a\" id=\"ua1a7447a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u22a8bd8b\" id=\"u22a8bd8b\">Object.is(1, 0)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u98dc22ca\" id=\"u98dc22ca\"> 为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua9f71189\" id=\"ua9f71189\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5e3a402e\" id=\"u5e3a402e\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf9c00876\" id=\"uf9c00876\">，依赖变化，重新执行 effect。</span></li><li fid=\"u9b71f4dd\" data-lake-id=\"u28d30164\" id=\"u28d30164\"><span data-lake-id=\"u734e8585\" id=\"u734e8585\">如果依赖项是对象：</span></li></ul><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20%5Buser%2C%20setUser%5D%20%3D%20useState(%7B%20name%3A%20'Alice'%20%7D)%3B%5CnuseEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20console.log(user.name)%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20%5Buser%5D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22DyXHx%22%7D\"></card><ul list=\"u45eea085\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u94103bab\" data-lake-id=\"u29e0cfd4\" id=\"u29e0cfd4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1ff85bd1\" id=\"u1ff85bd1\">即使 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u4a3601f3\" id=\"u4a3601f3\"><span data-lake-id=\"uda826b49\" id=\"uda826b49\">user</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3addc8e8\" id=\"u3addc8e8\"> 对象内容不变，但调用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5d512ee3\" id=\"u5d512ee3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u28acaf1b\" id=\"u28acaf1b\">setUser({ name: 'Alice' })</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8519654e\" id=\"u8519654e\"> 传入新对象时，新旧引用不同，</span><code data-lake-id=\"u6fda6d30\" id=\"u6fda6d30\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5afc5699\" id=\"u5afc5699\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u70e69b45\" id=\"u70e69b45\"> 返回 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u36d198d6\" id=\"u36d198d6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9a9eae35\" id=\"u9a9eae35\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0511cde3\" id=\"u0511cde3\">，effect 会执行。这可能导致不必要的 effect 执行，因此需要稳定依赖（如使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u17829656\" id=\"u17829656\"><span data-lake-id=\"u005de315\" id=\"u005de315\">useMemo</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uae503473\" id=\"uae503473\">/</span><code data-lake-id=\"uc86b6bf6\" id=\"uc86b6bf6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u79eded00\" id=\"u79eded00\">useCallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue7e25048\" id=\"ue7e25048\"> 或基于值的比较）。</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22XrRnx%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"lHp1R\" id=\"lHp1R\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5aa4e3b8\" id=\"u5aa4e3b8\">6. 依赖项存储位置</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"ued482cbb\" id=\"ued482cbb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u28300bff\" id=\"u28300bff\">React 在内部将每个 effect 的信息（包括上一次的依赖项）存储在对应 Fiber 节点的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u93d6a325\" id=\"u93d6a325\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc6c0ef97\" id=\"uc6c0ef97\">memoizedState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u84f6b433\" id=\"u84f6b433\"> 链表中。每个 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufc626ec4\" id=\"ufc626ec4\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubb02899d\" id=\"ubb02899d\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u009f0264\" id=\"u009f0264\"> 对应一个 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u12df8b14\" id=\"u12df8b14\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0ce715fb\" id=\"u0ce715fb\">Effect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8172c240\" id=\"u8172c240\"> 对象，其中包含：</span></p><ul list=\"u363bfaaf\"><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"uf268647b\" id=\"uf268647b\"><code data-lake-id=\"u2b1649e4\" id=\"u2b1649e4\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub398da4c\" id=\"ub398da4c\">create</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0625b798\" id=\"u0625b798\">: effect 函数</span></li><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"ue600ba12\" id=\"ue600ba12\"><code data-lake-id=\"u61b507f9\" id=\"u61b507f9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5c01751b\" id=\"u5c01751b\">destroy</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uea2e354c\" id=\"uea2e354c\">: 清理函数</span></li><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"u031d1a7b\" id=\"u031d1a7b\"><code data-lake-id=\"u1f7b1e03\" id=\"u1f7b1e03\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue8b04c0e\" id=\"ue8b04c0e\">deps</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u960541d1\" id=\"u960541d1\">: 上一次的依赖项数组</span></li><li fid=\"udc342a77\" data-lake-id=\"ua022a2ec\" id=\"ua022a2ec\"><code data-lake-id=\"ue79994ec\" id=\"ue79994ec\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5c01f9c8\" id=\"u5c01f9c8\">next</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u85e0af87\" id=\"u85e0af87\">: 指向下一个 effect 的指针</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ueeae5ccc\" id=\"ueeae5ccc\"><span data-lake-id=\"uedb40b99\" id=\"uedb40b99\">更新时，React 从链表中取出上一次的依赖项，与当前传入的依赖项进行 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1c71b332\" id=\"u1c71b332\"><span data-lake-id=\"u724c0119\" id=\"u724c0119\">Object.is</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u35bf5656\" id=\"u35bf5656\"> 比较。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22i0fqj%22%7D\"></card><h2 data-lake-id=\"j86Wl\" id=\"j86Wl\"><span data-lake-id=\"u06a74311\" id=\"u06a74311\">总结</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u8f1ad501\" id=\"u8f1ad501\"><code data-lake-id=\"ub0a31a13\" id=\"ub0a31a13\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue2a3f0c4\" id=\"ue2a3f0c4\">useEffect</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2f77f7e8\" id=\"u2f77f7e8\"> 的依赖比较基于 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u145c5603\" id=\"u145c5603\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc523c3cc\" id=\"uc523c3cc\">Object.is</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u66b34a00\" id=\"u66b34a00\"> 进行浅比较</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"udcd90429\" id=\"udcd90429\">，只有所有依赖项都与上一次相同时才跳过 effect。理解这一机制有助于避免因引用变化导致的无限循环，以及优化 effect 的执行频率。</span></p>","word_count":917,"slug":"hs65sqb71k2gx2o2","type":"Doc","title":"useEffect的第二个参数，是如何判断实现依赖是否发生变化的？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"useEffect 的第二个参数是依赖项数组，React 通过它来判断是否需要重新执行 effect。判断依赖是否发生变化的核心机制是浅比较，具体规则如下：1. 比较时机每次组件渲染完成后（即 commit 阶段的 layout 之后，浏览器绘制之前），React 会检查该 effect 的依...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"hr\":7,\"codeblock\":2}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-03-03T03:07:05.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-03-03T03:09:36.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-03-03T03:09:36.157Z","content_updated_at":"2026-03-03T03:09:36.000Z","id":259246114},"doc_digest":"Sp8Lvy1uYD7igbLYZSohPrMPr2o"}